Client -> Server : select weapon + aim + fire ( commit , aka selection done we locked in decision )

select bazooka
{
  "t": "turn.command",
  "matchId": "m_42",
  "turnNumber": 7,
  "clientCommandId": "c3",
  "cmd": { "type": "SELECT_WEAPON", "weaponId": "bazooka" }
}
aim ( optional , if we want reconnect , spectators, obeservers we can have it )
{
  "t": "turn.command",
  "matchId": "m_42",
  "turnNumber": 7,
  "clientCommandId": "c4",
  "cmd": { "type": "SET_AIM", "angleDeg": 35.0, "power": 0.78 }
}
fire ( real moment when we commit )

{
  "t": "turn.command",
  "matchId": "m_42",
  "turnNumber": 7,
  "clientCommandId": "c5",
  "cmd": { "type": "FIRE", "weaponId": "bazooka", "angleDeg": 35.0, "power": 0.78 }
}

Server -> Clients : phase change to Resolve + projectile spawn for everybody 

{
  "t": "turn.events",
  "matchId": "m_42",
  "turnNumber": 7,
  "seqFrom": 1203,
  "events": [
    { "type": "WEAPON_SELECTED", "wormId": "wA1", "weaponId": "bazooka" },
    { "type": "AIM_SET", "wormId": "wA1", "angleDeg": 35.0, "power": 0.78 },

    { "type": "PHASE_CHANGED", "phase": "RESOLVE" },

    {
      "type": "PROJECTILE_SPAWNED",
      "projId": "pr_9001",
      "kind": "bazooka_rocket",
      "origin": [13.05, 5.35],
      "velocity": [7.20, 6.10],

      "animHint": {
        "clientSimMs": 2200,
        "sampleEveryMs": 100
      }
    }
  ],
  "seqTo": 1206,
  "ack": ["c3", "c4", "c5"],
  "stateHashAfter": "h_mid_7"
}
Clients can  do a local pretty trajectory animation , server decides the hit 

Server -> Clients : explosion + terrain deformation + damage ( milestones ) 

A second big packages when projectile hits
